      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEAR NOT FRANKY (3) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Grade 5 at this track. Good beginner and aided by a handy draw. Better than last run and makes appeal this time. STAND GUARD (1) turned in a plain effort last time when sixth at this track over 400m behind Julie Keeping (23.58) in a Grade 5. Better than last start and can bounce back. KIANDO ESTATE (6) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (19.16) in a Grade 5 at this track. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Likely to be thereabouts. ABLE RIVAL (7) has strong claims after a long-odds top-three finish last time out.",
